<body class="kitchen-listing-body">
<%= render("shared/menu") %>

<div class="listing-container">
  <section class="listing-head-container clearfix">
    <h2 class="listing-title">Large Downtown Kitchen</h2>
    <ul class="listing-details-list">
      <li>Portland, OR, USA</li>
      <li>465 Square Meters</li>
      <li>2 Reviews</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="listing-date-container clearfix">
    <form class="listing-dates-form">
      <label class="listing-date-label" for="start-date">Dates</label>
      <input class="listing-start-date" title="start-date" type="date" id="start-date">
      <input class="listing-end-date" title="end-date" type="date">
    </form>
    <div class="listing-price-container">
        <span class="listing-price">
          <span class="price-math">$460/week * 2 weeks =</span>
          <span class="listing-total-price">$920</span>
        </span>
      <button class="transparent-button listing-book-button">
        Request Kitchen
      </button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="listing-images-container">
    <%= image_tag "sampleKitchens/3.jpeg", class: "listing-image" %>
  </section>

  <section class="listing-details-container">
    <article class="listing-description">
      <h2 class="listing-details-heading">Description</h2>
      <p>
        Bacon ipsum dolor amet brisket ground round turkey pastrami, pork sausage drumstick. Frankfurter turkey chicken
        pork chop cow spare ribs beef short loin tail ham hock biltong. Ribeye andouille short loin, pork loin sausage
        shoulder bresaola turkey. Beef ribs tongue flank, jerky rump cow cupim picanha pork loin fatback. Pancetta
        kielbasa ham hock sausage landjaeger.
      </p>
      <p>
        Meatloaf ham hamburger shoulder pork belly venison fatback shankle pork bresaola prosciutto. Pig short loin
        swine prosciutto ball tip drumstick ribeye pork loin tri-tip pork chop. Turkey beef ribs beef kevin flank. Kevin
        leberkas bresaola frankfurter pig tri-tip andouille. Beef turducken filet mignon, ribeye tongue kielbasa
        bresaola shank ground round meatloaf bacon. Turkey cupim ground round chuck pork belly pork chop. Picanha ham
        hock leberkas, kevin drumstick alcatra beef bacon brisket.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="listing-features">
      <h2 class="listing-details-heading">Features</h2>
      <ul class="listing-features-list">
        <li>Moorwood Vulcan 6 burner double oven</li>
        <li>Large freestanding Foster freezer</li>
        <li>Large freestanding Foster fridge</li>
        <li>Two double sinks</li>
        <li>Wash hand basin</li>
        <li>Large static warming cupboard</li>
        <li>Deep fat fryer</li>
        <li>Dishwasher</li>
        <li>9m preparation area</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </section>
</div>
</body>
</html>
